#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:130
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-planned-additions.adoc:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Publishing sampling-event data"
msgstr "サンプリングイベントデータの公開"

#. type: Title ===
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:132
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-planned-additions.adoc:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using GUIDs for identifiers"
msgstr "識別子にGUIDを使用する"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:135
msgid "A number of fields require the usage of unique identifiers: dwc:occurrenceID, dwc:eventID, dwc:organismID and dwc:locationID."
msgstr "dwc:occurrenceID、dwc:eventID、dwc:organismID、dwc:locationIDなどのフィールドは、一意な識別子を必要とします。"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:137
msgid "As mentioned previously, although no particular format is enforced, we advise publishers to use Global Unique IDentifiers (GUIDs). There are a few online services which can provide such identifiers. For example, it is possible to use http://www.geonames.org/ to find (or even generate new) identifiers for dwc:locationID, e.g. http://sws.geonames.org/10793757/ is a GUID for a lake in Greenland."
msgstr "前述の通り、特定のフォーマットは強制されませんが、出版社にはGlobal Unique IDentifiers（GUID）を使用するようアドバイスしています。そのような識別子を提供するオンラインサービスがいくつかあります。例えば、http://www.geonames.org/ を使って dwc:locationID の識別子を見つける（あるいは新しい識別子を生成する）ことができます。例えば、http://sws.geonames.org/10793757/ はグリーンランドの湖の GUID です。"

#. type: Title ===
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "Protect location of sensitive species"
msgstr "影響を受けやすい生物種の地理情報を保護する"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:141
msgid "If your dataset contains sensitive species, there are several ways to handle it:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:143
msgid "Simply removing these species from the dataset,"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:144
msgid "Publishing the species identifications at Genus level only,"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:145
msgid "Publishing the sensitive/protected species in a separate dataset,"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:146
msgid "Publish obfuscated sensitive data points in the main dataset and publish non-obfuscated details in an access-limited separate dataset, both datasets including all data records."
msgstr ""

